<br>
-Harmaa <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F5F5DC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub96.ezboard.com/uwhelpofkb.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whelp of KB</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Baron Whelp, Image Master</span><br>  Posts: 35<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/2/02 8:43:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub96.ezboard.com/fkanebaylecommunitycenterfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: LFG Channel?</span><hr size=1> Break it down into lvl ranges perhaps? Like /lfg30-40 or something. Don't really need every newbie and his dog spamming the same channel as a lvl 50 for a space at orc1 <p>~ Local scrawny whelp..."Please don't kick me"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub96.ezboard.com/uharmaa.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Harmaa</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Level 2, Generic Newbie</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/2/02 8:50:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub96.ezboard.com/fkanebaylecommunitycenterfrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: LFG Channel?</span><hr size=1> I don't think that breaking it into levels is necessary. I think that the channel will end up being used for level 50+ people. At that level there will be more of an actual need for certain classes in a group and it's actually worth traveling a few zones or continents to get to a group.<br>
<br>
